1
00:00:50,780 --> 00:00:55,740
=Sugar and Lies=
(A Different Her: The Women's Trilogy)

2
00:00:56,820 --> 00:00:59,780
=Episode 10=
=Ten Thousand Chances to Meet=

3
00:01:11,760 --> 00:01:12,600
Sorry about that.

4
00:01:13,200 --> 00:01:14,040
It's fine, really.

5
00:01:14,480 --> 00:01:15,320
Not a big deal.

6
00:01:15,880 --> 00:01:16,800
Oh, that won't do.

7
00:01:19,080 --> 00:01:19,920
How about this?

8
00:01:20,400 --> 00:01:21,520
This coffee's on me.

9
00:01:22,000 --> 00:01:23,160
And I'll find a dry cleaner

10
00:01:23,400 --> 00:01:24,580
and have your clothes cleaned.

11
00:01:32,400 --> 00:01:33,760
Do you honestly feel that guilty?

12
00:01:39,400 --> 00:01:40,800
Then stay with me for five minutes.

13
00:01:42,240 --> 00:01:43,320
Because...

14
00:01:43,920 --> 00:01:44,880
I feel a bit uneasy.

15
00:01:47,120 --> 00:01:47,960
What's going on?

16
00:01:49,120 --> 00:01:50,760
Are you feeling unwell?

17
00:01:54,240 --> 00:01:55,520
Let me you to the hospital?

18
00:02:00,000 --> 00:02:01,400
Not sure which hospital

19
00:02:02,600 --> 00:02:03,600
treats loneliness.

20
00:02:10,120 --> 00:02:11,520
Your way of starting a conversation

21
00:02:12,920 --> 00:02:13,760
is pretty unique.

22
00:02:16,240 --> 00:02:17,000
I'm Miaomiao.

23
00:02:17,000 --> 00:02:18,080
Miao with six water strokes.

24
00:02:18,680 --> 00:02:19,920
Wanna get to know each other?

25
00:02:24,400 --> 00:02:25,280
I'm Hu Yitong.

26
00:02:27,200 --> 00:02:28,960
Your parents must love playing mahjong.

27
00:02:31,600 --> 00:02:32,520
Hu.

28
00:02:32,520 --> 00:02:33,400
Yi.

29
00:02:33,400 --> 00:02:34,240
Tong.

30
00:02:48,160 --> 00:02:49,120
That is

31
00:02:49,560 --> 00:02:50,520
how we met.

32
00:02:53,640 --> 00:02:55,960
We had some amazing times together.

33
00:02:59,560 --> 00:03:01,080
But we broke up soon after.

34
00:03:02,040 --> 00:03:03,300
Miaomiao was great in every way.

35
00:03:04,600 --> 00:03:05,880
She just got a little too clingy.

36
00:03:07,200 --> 00:03:08,400
When I was with her,

37
00:03:09,520 --> 00:03:11,960
I often felt trapped underwater.

38
00:03:14,600 --> 00:03:16,520
Even breathing felt like a crime.

39
00:03:17,740 --> 00:03:20,140
(Even you turned your back on me.
Leaving is my only choice.)

40
00:03:30,960 --> 00:03:32,040
In my whole life,

41
00:03:32,360 --> 00:03:33,720
everyone keeps leaving me behind.

42
00:03:34,200 --> 00:03:35,440
Dad walked away from me.

43
00:03:35,960 --> 00:03:37,240
Then Mom left me too.

44
00:03:37,800 --> 00:03:39,140
My brother turned his back on me.

45
00:03:39,440 --> 00:03:41,280
And now you're leaving me as well.

46
00:03:41,720 --> 00:03:44,200
Leaving is the only choice I have.

47
00:03:47,560 --> 00:03:48,400
Miaomiao.

48
00:03:49,200 --> 00:03:50,200
Chen Miaomiao.

49
00:04:02,200 --> 00:04:03,280
You're losing it.

50
00:04:07,300 --> 00:04:08,990
We've been together for barely half a year.

51
00:04:10,560 --> 00:04:11,720
And things like this

52
00:04:13,000 --> 00:04:15,080
happen almost every month.

53
00:04:17,120 --> 00:04:18,440
I'm honestly exhausted.

54
00:04:20,080 --> 00:04:20,920
I'm drained.

55
00:04:22,080 --> 00:04:23,360
Then I met Ding Daang.

56
00:04:24,840 --> 00:04:26,400
That's when I realized there are

57
00:04:27,520 --> 00:04:28,980
still people in this world like her,

58
00:04:29,920 --> 00:04:30,760
open-hearted,

59
00:04:31,720 --> 00:04:32,560
reasonable,

60
00:04:33,960 --> 00:04:34,880
and genuinely lovely.

61
00:04:34,880 --> 00:04:35,760
That's enough!

62
00:04:37,040 --> 00:04:37,880
Shut up.

63
00:04:41,880 --> 00:04:42,720
Yu Kun.

64
00:04:44,320 --> 00:04:45,480
What are you so afraid of?

65
00:04:46,800 --> 00:04:48,720
If something really happens to Miaomiao,

66
00:04:50,360 --> 00:04:51,590
you should take responsibility.

67
00:04:52,760 --> 00:04:55,120
Because the one who hurt her the most

68
00:04:56,280 --> 00:04:57,760
is you, her own brother.

69
00:04:59,600 --> 00:05:00,440
Brother.

70
00:05:01,040 --> 00:05:01,880
It's me.

71
00:05:02,280 --> 00:05:03,120
Miaomiao.

72
00:05:07,080 --> 00:05:07,920
Brother.

73
00:05:08,360 --> 00:05:09,200
Hold on.

74
00:05:09,960 --> 00:05:12,120
All visitors must register
with the company.

75
00:05:13,200 --> 00:05:14,040
Unrelated individuals

76
00:05:14,040 --> 00:05:15,200
are not allowed to enter here.

77
00:05:15,520 --> 00:05:16,480
Don't disrupt our work.

78
00:05:21,640 --> 00:05:23,440
Is that really your excuse for cheating?

79
00:05:24,640 --> 00:05:26,360
I have more than enough evidence

80
00:05:26,680 --> 00:05:27,520
to prove that

81
00:05:27,760 --> 00:05:28,600
you were dating

82
00:05:29,080 --> 00:05:29,960
Ding Daang

83
00:05:31,800 --> 00:05:33,560
and Miaomiao at the same time.

84
00:05:34,080 --> 00:05:37,080
You're just a jerk
who played both sides.

85
00:05:40,920 --> 00:05:41,800
So

86
00:05:43,560 --> 00:05:44,480
what do you want?

87
00:05:46,000 --> 00:05:48,200
It was Miaomiao who kept clinging to me.

88
00:05:49,440 --> 00:05:51,000
You came back trying every trick

89
00:05:51,000 --> 00:05:52,540
to break me and Ding Daang apart,

90
00:05:53,640 --> 00:05:55,390
but it didn't bring me and Miaomiao together.

91
00:05:55,400 --> 00:05:56,240
Enough!

92
00:06:07,400 --> 00:06:08,560
So you came back

93
00:06:08,560 --> 00:06:09,400
to run away with me

94
00:06:10,360 --> 00:06:11,520
for Miaomiao's sake?

95
00:06:21,320 --> 00:06:22,440
Of course not.

96
00:06:26,960 --> 00:06:29,600
I just wanted you to see
what kind of guy he really is.

97
00:06:35,960 --> 00:06:37,280
You knew everything all along,

98
00:06:38,000 --> 00:06:39,320
but you never told me.

99
00:06:41,960 --> 00:06:43,240
What do you take me for?

100
00:06:45,000 --> 00:06:47,680
Some tool to get back at Hu Yitong?

101
00:06:50,600 --> 00:06:51,800
Miaomiao is my sister.

102
00:06:53,920 --> 00:06:54,840
I can't just stand by

103
00:06:54,840 --> 00:06:56,640
and watch her slipping deeper
into the dark.

104
00:06:56,960 --> 00:06:57,960
Then what about me?

105
00:07:00,200 --> 00:07:01,040
Ding Daang.

106
00:07:03,080 --> 00:07:04,360
I already gave you a choice.

107
00:07:06,600 --> 00:07:07,440
Now,

108
00:07:09,880 --> 00:07:10,840
it's up to you.

109
00:07:16,800 --> 00:07:17,840
A choice?

110
00:07:18,360 --> 00:07:19,600
How am I supposed to choose?

111
00:07:21,680 --> 00:07:22,920
Should I choose him,

112
00:07:22,920 --> 00:07:24,720
a two-timing jerk,

113
00:07:25,000 --> 00:07:26,120
or should I choose you,

114
00:07:26,120 --> 00:07:27,840
the liar who used me all along?

115
00:07:42,960 --> 00:07:44,080
Get out of my shop.

116
00:07:44,320 --> 00:07:45,160
Out.

117
00:07:47,040 --> 00:07:48,640
Ding Daang, listen to me.

118
00:07:48,640 --> 00:07:49,480
Ding Daang.

119
00:07:51,440 --> 00:07:52,280
Ding Daang.

120
00:07:56,440 --> 00:07:57,480
Get out of my shop!

121
00:07:57,600 --> 00:07:58,760
Get out of my shop!

122
00:08:07,080 --> 00:08:07,920
Get out!

123
00:08:11,380 --> 00:08:14,100
(Suga Love)

124
00:08:17,440 --> 00:08:18,280
Yu Kun.

125
00:08:19,360 --> 00:08:21,120
Your data can be inaccurate sometimes.

126
00:08:22,840 --> 00:08:23,680
Keep working.

127
00:08:24,680 --> 00:08:25,960
How I handle things

128
00:08:27,280 --> 00:08:28,120
is not your business.

129
00:08:30,280 --> 00:08:31,680
You know exactly

130
00:08:33,440 --> 00:08:34,800
what you've done.

131
00:08:36,450 --> 00:08:37,500
If you dare to stop

132
00:08:37,510 --> 00:08:39,040
my engagement ceremony with Ding Daang,

133
00:08:39,880 --> 00:08:41,040
the one paying the price

134
00:08:43,080 --> 00:08:44,200
might be your Keep Love.

135
00:08:46,280 --> 00:08:47,320
So you're threatening me?

136
00:08:52,640 --> 00:08:54,040
If I'm not mistaken,

137
00:08:56,520 --> 00:08:57,880
my chance encounter with Miaomiao

138
00:08:58,800 --> 00:08:59,840
was your setup, wasn't it?

139
00:09:01,120 --> 00:09:02,880
Miaomiao was one of your subjects too.

140
00:09:04,360 --> 00:09:05,240
My breakup with her

141
00:09:06,600 --> 00:09:08,160
made the success rate of your experiment

142
00:09:08,160 --> 00:09:09,440
fall short of 100%.

143
00:09:10,680 --> 00:09:12,640
You next round of funding could fail.

144
00:09:13,760 --> 00:09:14,640
So,

145
00:09:16,760 --> 00:09:18,320
you came to Ding Daang

146
00:09:20,080 --> 00:09:21,400
purely for your career, right?

147
00:09:27,120 --> 00:09:27,960
Hu Yitong,

148
00:09:28,960 --> 00:09:30,560
I have no idea what you're talking about.

149
00:09:32,000 --> 00:09:33,880
Please stop making things up.

150
00:09:39,240 --> 00:09:40,280
Honestly, I'm glad

151
00:09:43,240 --> 00:09:44,400
I didn't end up being a family

152
00:09:45,680 --> 00:09:47,120
with someone like you, who'd turn

153
00:09:49,520 --> 00:09:50,690
their back on their own blood.

154
00:10:02,400 --> 00:10:03,240
Boss,

155
00:10:03,240 --> 00:10:04,280
Chen Miaomiao is

156
00:10:04,280 --> 00:10:05,880
our twenty-third volunteer.

157
00:10:06,240 --> 00:10:07,680
She's a perfect subject.

158
00:10:12,920 --> 00:10:13,760
Xibei,

159
00:10:13,760 --> 00:10:15,520
how's the matching result?

160
00:10:16,780 --> 00:10:19,420
(Name: Hu Yitong. Basic Information)

161
00:10:24,400 --> 00:10:25,660
Where am I supposed to find him?

162
00:10:27,160 --> 00:10:29,120
Always trust Keep Love.

163
00:10:29,520 --> 00:10:31,560
It can create a thousand different ways

164
00:10:31,560 --> 00:10:32,760
to bump into him by chance.

165
00:10:32,760 --> 00:10:33,600
Keep Love

166
00:10:34,440 --> 00:10:36,080
even scripts your encounter,

167
00:10:36,760 --> 00:10:38,200
so you can say exactly

168
00:10:38,200 --> 00:10:39,280
what he's longing to hear.

169
00:10:42,800 --> 00:10:43,640
Congratulations,

170
00:10:45,360 --> 00:10:46,200
Miaomiao.

171
00:10:47,120 --> 00:10:48,520
You're about to start

172
00:10:49,000 --> 00:10:51,040
your love journey
under the help of Keep Love.

173
00:10:52,360 --> 00:10:53,200
I'm Miaomiao.

174
00:10:54,800 --> 00:10:55,960
I'm Hu Yitong.

175
00:10:59,600 --> 00:11:00,720
Is it really worth it?

176
00:11:01,360 --> 00:11:03,480
When he left back then,
you were like this too.

177
00:11:04,480 --> 00:11:05,600
It's been so many years.

178
00:11:06,760 --> 00:11:08,920
Why can't you just let yourself move on?

179
00:11:10,240 --> 00:11:11,080
Ding Daang,

180
00:11:12,520 --> 00:11:13,640
you're still defending him.

181
00:11:15,840 --> 00:11:17,320
You're defending this jerk?

182
00:11:18,800 --> 00:11:19,640
Let go.

183
00:11:20,000 --> 00:11:21,680
Believe it or not, I might hit you too.

184
00:11:23,520 --> 00:11:24,360
Come on then, do it.

185
00:11:26,640 --> 00:11:28,000
It's not like you haven't before.

186
00:11:53,210 --> 00:12:00,210
♪I forgot this is a movie meant for one♪

187
00:12:04,610 --> 00:12:11,970
♪Somehow you're still here,
crying with me♪

188
00:12:16,420 --> 00:12:18,360
♪They say♪

189
00:12:18,770 --> 00:12:27,150
♪Lovers should never hold hands
while watching a sad movie♪

190
00:12:27,670 --> 00:12:30,650
♪Some endings cannot be changed♪

191
00:12:30,870 --> 00:12:36,820
♪They don't belong in sweet memories♪

192
00:12:38,200 --> 00:12:43,960
♪I've already lost you♪

193
00:12:43,960 --> 00:12:49,440
♪Thinking of it takes my breath away♪

194
00:12:49,740 --> 00:12:55,690
♪The movie ends, so many couples around♪

195
00:12:55,690 --> 00:13:00,470
♪Yet none were ever like us♪

196
00:13:01,580 --> 00:13:05,610
♪The past will always pass♪

197
00:13:05,940 --> 00:13:13,520
♪If you could still hold me tight
in your arms♪

198
00:13:13,990 --> 00:13:17,240
♪I'd believe
that there are miracles in love♪

199
00:13:17,800 --> 00:13:23,450
♪I'd prove
that I'm still in love with you♪

200
00:13:25,910 --> 00:13:29,440
♪I've learned how to cherish
what we had♪

201
00:13:29,440 --> 00:13:35,700
♪But sadly, it's not you♪
